transcript:
Customer: Hello.

Executive: Hello. Haan sir.
Executive: Main IndiaMART se baat kar raha hu, Himanshu kaise hai?
Customer: Abhi baad mein phone kariye.
Executive: Sir, main ek baat jaanna cha raha tha aapka feedback hai aapko kuch ke regarding ki kya dikkat aa rahi hai aapke services mein aur aapke sab sahi chal raha hai.
Customer: Baad mein baat kariye, main court mein hu jara.
Executive: Achcha court mein, achcha achcha achcha, theek hai sir.
